n by LISA as eccentric sources and, a few years later, as circular\nsources by LIGO and the Einstein Telescope, making decihertz observatories like\nDECIGO unique instruments to bridge the observations during the binary\ninspiral.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 19:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-17"}
