ely the temporal profile of cytokines and VENG changes. This\nnovel model allows manipulating and tracking neonatal sepsis: The HRV\ninflammatory index 1) applies across species pre- and postnatally and 2)\nperforms well at different degrees of sepsis (i.e., nanogram and milligram\ndoses of LPS); 3) the present VNS paradigm effectively suppresses LPS-induced\ninflammation, even at high doses of LPS. The potential of early postnatal VNS\nto counteract sepsis and of HRV monitoring to early detect and track it deserve\nfurther study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 23:43:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Dec 2022 18:54:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-21"}
