 the\nlayered GO films from 2D monolayers to quasi bulk like behavior. These results\nconfirm the high nonlinear optical performance of integrated photonic\nresonators incorporated with 2D layered GO films.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 01:17:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
