ty has an optimal dependence on the parameters $n$ and $\\epsilon$, as\nwell as if $k=1$ on the strong positivity parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 07:15:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2020 06:11:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-07"}
