 accurate MAP\nestimate for the primary current density was obtained in both superficial and\ndeep parts of the brain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 09:22:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Feb 2020 09:52:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-24"}
